title: Arsenal go top of the Premier League with hard-working home victory over Everton - Thurrock Gazette
text:
Arsenal moved to the top of the Barclays Premier League following a hard-earned 2-1 win over Everton at the Emirates Stadium. Two goals inside as many minutes in the first half from Olivier Giroud and Laurent Koscielny looked to have set the Gunners up for a comfortable evening.
 Thurrock Gazette.
